//   - HookEvent (LUA_HOOKCALL / LUA_HOOKLINE / LUA_HOOKCOUNT constants)
//   - LuaStatus (LUA_OK / LUA_YIELD / LUA_ERRRUN)
//   - luaF_getlocalname — from crate::func
